metadata.name: Costumava ser aqui
metadata.description:
It used to be here

I return to the past to observe it and decide what I leave and what I continue to carry with me. 

Clothes: I chose an outfit that fulfilled my mother's wishes. She always wanted me to be more feminine, to wear pink and short dresses, but since I was five years old, I didn't feel comfortable wearing a dress or pink.

Location: I chose a happy place from childhood that even now remains a place of peace.
